{"tid":1918402,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平前往火神山醫院探望正接受治療的患者","createTime":"2020-03-10T05:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T15:18:15.000Z","uid":212626,"like":102,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"13f342213a12164dd8596b584973baa02c25d400","tid":1918402,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:34:31.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平上午乘坐飛機抵達湖北武漢，考察湖北和武漢防控新型冠狀病毒疫情的工作。中央電視台報道，習近平到埗後就前往火神山醫院，了解醫院建設運行、患者收治、醫務人員防護保障、科研攻關等，又探望正接受治療的患者，慰問前線醫務工作者，勉勵大家堅定信心，戰勝疫情。<br />\n<br />\n習近平又會探望和慰問解放軍指戰員、公安等幹部和志願者，以及社區居民。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1272726&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1272726%26csid%3D261_341&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=5b413bfd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1272726&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426a5a4ebd25db8d6881ae6fd5858963b810c68a","tid":1918402,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfdca7832b281d84607682b5979a7ef1896e79d","tid":1918402,"uid":155095,"like":86,"dislike":1,"score":85,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/IHIHQfb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FIHIHQfb.png&h=c5db6ab4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eee0ed61026d37cbc36b7f82c574e4c2b3c8a641","tid":1918402,"uid":285037,"like":198,"dislike":3,"score":195,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"放心 患者會搵演員扮<br />\n確保維尼不會受感染"},{"pid":"afbfa35681a35d2e5f2c1