3-10T10:32:44.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">李克強去昭通年貨市場，到肉攤前問：「生意怎麼樣？」答：「平時挺好，今天一斤沒賣。」李：「為什麼？」答：「因為您來了顧客不讓進。」李：「那我買兩斤。」答：「不賣。」李：「為什麼？」答：「因為您來了，刀不讓帶。」李：「刀沒帶也行，就買這一塊兒。」答：「那也不能賣。」李：「為什麼？」答：「因為你沒來時每斤23元，你來了每斤18元，賣1斤虧5元。」李：「那就按每斤23元來一塊兒。」答：「那也不賣。」李大驚：「又為啥？」答：「我不是賣肉的，我其實是個武警。」李：「把你支隊長叫來！」答：「支隊長在賣昭通蘋果。」</code></pre>"},{"pid":"831f7da0eddbca14f087ca75979f0f69962f5e58","tid":1918402,"uid":264892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eee0ed61026d37cbc36b7f82c574e4c2b3c8a641","tid":1918402,"uid":285037,"like":198,"dislike":3,"score":195,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"放心 患者會搵演員扮<br />\n確保維尼不會受感染"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T10:36:30.000Z","msg":"維尼點會去武漢<br />\n要扮梗係直接扮維尼啦"},{"pid":"d229868f297f5221d183a3435976d6905881a90f","tid":1918402,"uid":319080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b7d8becc37c7e66428ee94ebb8ee3f0e7546ce","tid":1918402,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e639af061c377060e634d7a91fe64a21f91d829","tid":1918402,"uid":40439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T10:28:21.000Z","msg":"層層樓都有狙擊手無人敢叫全部都是假的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1237299449015103488?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRFA_Chinese%2Fstatus%2F1237299449015103488%3Fs%3D09&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSohgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=a9a7835c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRFA_Chinese%2Fstatus%2F1237299449015103488%3Fs%3D09&h=e9a746cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RFA_Chinese/status/1237299449015103488?s=09</a>"},